                        <interp inst="t18390812-name-527" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM LEA</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a police-constable. I saw the prisoner and an<lb></lb>other running—I took the prisoner—the other made his escape—I told him I took him for stealing the money from Mr. Salmon's till—he said</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183908120058"></xptr>
               <p>he did not know any thing about it—I found three shillings and three thimbles on him.</p>
